  "title": "Funeral Services Sales Representative",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Conduct strategic project planning sessions, ensuring alignment across internal teams and external partners.</li>\n  <li>Direct end-to-end project management, maintaining timelines, budgets, and deliverables.</li>\n  <li>Produce precise and up-to-date project documentation for clarity and accountability.</li>\n  <li>Evaluate project outcomes, measuring success and identifying optimization opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Anticipate and address risks through structured mitigation plans.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Business Growth &amp; Strategy</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maximize deal value by driving strategic negotiations and partnerships.</li>\n  <li>Establish scalable processes for the new business unit to enhance efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Advise leadership on tender evaluations, project execution, and partnership opportunities.</li>\n  <li>Strengthen key alliances to foster long-term business growth.</li>\n  <li>Spearhead the development and rollout of new products/services in line with corporate strategy.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Performance &amp; Oversight</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Champion high-potential brands and business units to accelerate growth.</li>\n  <li>Provide executive-level updates on project milestones, challenges, and results.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
